<i>noun</i>: 횡행 [횡행/휑행], 성행 [성ː행] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>횡행 [횡행/휑행]</dt><br>
<dd>rampancy; prevalence</dd><br>
<dd>아무 거리낌 없이 제멋대로 행동함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of acting as one pleases without reserve.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성행 [성ː행]</dt><br>
<dd>prevalence</dd><br>
<dd>매우 왕성하게 유행함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being very popular.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>